Package: EDI
Type: Package
Title: Experimental Design and Inference
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Adam",
                  family = "Kapelner",
                  role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
                  email = "kapelner@qc.cuny.edu",
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5985-6792")))
Description: Provides a vast array of experimental designs (both fixed and sequential) focusing on matching-on-the-fly techniques to maintain covariate balance for response types continuous, incidence, count, proportion, survival and ordinal. It then provides a vast array of inference types specific to the design and the response type (exact, asymptotic and distribution-free). The package provides full support for missing data. The package is fully optimized using Rcpp.
